            "heading": "4,800+",
            "description": "Happy families trust us for their children's everyday wardrobe — and thousands more discover us every month."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "feature_card",
          "settings": {
            "bg_color": "#D94030",
            "text_color": "#ffffff",
            "icon_svg": "<svg viewBox='0 0 24 24'><rect x='1' y='3' width='15' height='13' rx='2'></rect><path d='M16 8h4l3 5v3h-7V8z'></path><circle cx='5.5' cy='18.5' r='2.5'></circle><circle cx='18.5' cy='18.5' r='2.5'></circle></svg>",
            "heading": "Delivered in 1–3 Days",
            "description": "Fast, tracked shipping straight to your door — so your child's new favourite outfit arrives just in time, every time."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "feature_card",
          "settings": {
            "bg_color": "#3B82D4",
            "text_color": "#ffffff",
            "icon_svg": "<svg viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z'></path></svg>",
            "heading": "Fits Through Every Growth Spurt",
            "description": "Flexible waistbands and stretch-fit designs built for how kids actually move — no uncomfortable tightness, just pure all-day comfort."
          }
        },
        {
